Package: libv8
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: V8 JavaScript engine - runtime library
 V8 is a high performance JavaScript engine written in C++.
 It is used in the web browser Chromium.
 .
 This package provides the dynamic library for V8.

Package: libv8-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libv8 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: V8 JavaScript engine - development files for V8
 V8 is a high performance JavaScript engine written in C++.
 It is used in the web browser Chromium.
 .
 This package provide development headers for V8.

